{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SpawnSingleItem}}
'''A_SpawnSingleItem''' (class<Actor> ''type'', int ''fail_singleplayer'' = 0, int ''fail_cooperative'' = 0, int ''fail_deathmatch'' = 0)<br />

Spawns an actor of class ''type'' at the position of one, and only one, of the actors of the same type as the calling actor. The three ''fail'' parameters are the chance not to actually spawn anything at all in the concerned gamemode; 0 means to always spawn, 256 to never spawn.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|SpecialSpot}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Spawn functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:SpawnSingleItem}}
